LanguageData.yayoEnding_intro: The planetary energy teleporter shoots a beam of light to the sky.\n\n
LanguageData.yayoEnding_ending:
A strange light covers you and your friends, and everyone has dissapeard to the sky in a flash.
Cosmic rays quickly passes you by.
No one know who made this teleporter, nor where this light will take you to.
This could be an escape route of other humans like us, or a casual travel device made by unkown alien civilization.
you have a sweet dream as you enter your slumber.

You'll find out when you wake up.

- Yayo's EndGame - Mod by. Latki(Art), Yayo(Dev)
